ry results, but tries to reactivate a very ancient method (due\nbasically to Riemann 1857) whose swing seems to have been somewhat\nunderestimated, at least outside of the conformal-mapping community.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Apr 2013 15:35:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-04-23"}
